title: Ibyerekeye Twebwe
description: Skillseed ni urubuga rugamije gufasha abanyeshuri binyuze mu ndimi zitandukanye no gukorana n’abandi ku rwego mpuzamahanga.
vision: Icyerekezo cyacu ni ugutanga uburezi buboneye kandi burimo bose binyuze mu ikoranabuhanga.
team: Turi itsinda ry’abatekinisiye, abarimu n’abahanzi bafite umuhate.
